ent/src/closecall.ts`\n    35→- Updated `packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`: added `ClosecallIDL` JSON import, `Closecall` type export, IDL re-export\n    36→- Created `packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`: `CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID` (from IDL address), `getCloseCallRoundPda()`, `getCloseCallConfigPda()`\n    37→- Updated `packages/game-engine/src/index.ts`: added closecall exports\n    38→\n    39→**Notes**:\n    40→- Spec said `packages/config/` but that package only has build configs (tsconfig, eslint). Program IDs live in `packages/game-engine/src/` per existing coinflip/lordofrngs pattern. Followed actual codebase pattern.\n    41→- `pnpm lint` (18 packages): 0 errors, only pre-existing warnings\n    42→- `pnpm typecheck` (18 packages): 0 errors\n    43→\n    44→## Iteration 2 — 2026-03-17T18:51:24Z — OK\n    45→- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    46→\n    47→## Iteration 3 — Backend account decoders\n    48→\n    49→**Item**: [backend] Add `DecodedCloseCallRound` and `DecodedCloseCallConfig` interfaces + decoder functions\n    50→\n    51→**Result**: PASS\n    52→\n    53→**Changes**:\n    54→- `services/backend/src/worker/account-decoder.ts`:\n    55→  - Added `ClosecallIDL` import from `@rng-utopia/anchor-client`\n    56→  - Instantiated `closecallCoder` BorshAccountsCoder\n    57→  - Added `closeCallPhaseToNumber()` helper (Open=0, Settled=1, Refunded=2)\n    58→  - Added `outcomeToNumber()` helper (Pending=0, Green=1, Red=2, Refund=3)\n    59→  - Added `DecodedCloseCallRound` interface (16 fields: roundId, server, phase, greenEntries, redEntries, greenPool, redPool, openPrice, openPriceExpo, closePrice, createdAt, bettingEndsAt, resolveDeadline, outcome, totalFee, bump)\n    60→  - Added `DecodedCloseCallConfig` interface (7 fields: authority, treasury, pythFeedId, bettingWindowSecs, maxEntriesPerSide, paused, bump)\n    61→  - Added `decodeCloseCallRound()` and `decodeCloseCallConfig()` functions with bnToBigInt conversion and enum mapping\n    62→  - Added