{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017iNErHeAxctQfct6jE1rKy","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. I've gathered all the information you need about the Close Call program interface. Here's the summary:\n\n## Close Call Program Interface Summary\n\n### Program ID\n**Constant**: `CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID`\n- **Value**: `8TXq2XyHsk5AAMkoyk5QtG25xyyY7rTMHXrJRHRwjUpA` (from IDL)\n- **Derived from**: `ClosecallIDL.address` in `game-engine/src/closecall.ts`\n\n### place_bet Instruction Accounts\n\nThe `place_bet` instruction requires exactly **4 accounts**:\n\n1. **player** — writable, signer\n   - The player placing the bet\n\n2. **config** — read-only (not writable)\n   - PDA with seeds: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n   - Global configuration account\n\n3. **round** — writable\n   - PDA with seeds: `[\"cc_round\", round_id]` where `round_id` is an 8-byte array\n   - The specific round account\n\n4. **system_program** — read-only\n   - Hardcoded: `11111111111111111111111111111111`\n\n### place_bet Instruction Arguments\n\nThree arguments:\n\n1. **round_id** — `[u8; 8]`\n   - Backend-generated random round ID\n\n2. **side** — `u8`\n   - `0` = Green (bull)\n   - `1` = Red (bear)\n\n3. **amount** — `u64`\n   - Bet amount in lamports\n\n### PDA Derivation Functions\n\nBoth functions are in `packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport function getCloseCallRoundPda(roundId: Uint8Array): [PublicKey, number]\n// Seeds: [Buffer.from(\"cc_round\"), Buffer.from(roundId)]\n\nexport function getCloseCallConfigPda(): [PublicKey, number]\n// Seeds: [Buffer.from(\"closecall_config\")]\n```\n\n### Key Type Definitions\n\nFrom the IDL, the round account structure includes:\n\n- **BetEntry**: `{ player: pubkey, amount_lamports: u64 }`\n- **Outcome**: enum with variants `Pending | Green | Red | Refund`\n- **CloseCallPhase**: enum with variants `Open | Settled | Refunded`\n\nThe files are:\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: af05cd02c7ad646ed (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42216\ntool_uses: 3\nduration_ms: 10693</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"69ec7f4b-ea2c-48d6-9a60-da2ab1703b1a","uuid":"ad6f72ce-c8d5-48a3-82bf-3a8706ccd1c6","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files to understand the closecall program interface:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json` (IDL - especially the place_bet instruction accounts)\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts` (program ID, PDA helpers)\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts` (how closecall is exported)\n\nI need to understand:\n- What accounts the `place_bet` instruction needs\n- The PDA derivation functions available\n- The program ID constant\n\nThoroughness: medium.","agentId":"af05cd02c7ad646ed","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. I've gathered all the information you need about the Close Call program interface. Here's the summary:\n\n## Close Call Program Interface Summary\n\n### Program ID\n**Constant**: `CLOSECALL_PROGRAM_ID`\n- **Value**: `8TXq2XyHsk5AAMkoyk5QtG25xyyY7rTMHXrJRHRwjUpA` (from IDL)\n- **Derived from**: `ClosecallIDL.address` in `game-engine/src/closecall.ts`\n\n### place_bet Instruction Accounts\n\nThe `place_bet` instruction requires exactly **4 accounts**:\n\n1. **player** — writable, signer\n   - The player placing the bet\n\n2. **config** — read-only (not writable)\n   - PDA with seeds: `[\"closecall_config\"]`\n   - Global configuration account\n\n3. **round** — writable\n   - PDA with seeds: `[\"cc_round\", round_id]` where `round_id` is an 8-byte array\n   - The specific round account\n\n4. **system_program** — read-only\n   - Hardcoded: `11111111111111111111111111111111`\n\n### place_bet Instruction Arguments\n\nThree arguments:\n\n1. **round_id** — `[u8; 8]`\n   - Backend-generated random round ID\n\n2. **side** — `u8`\n   - `0` = Green (bull)\n   - `1` = Red (bear)\n\n3. **amount** — `u64`\n   - Bet amount in lamports\n\n### PDA Derivation Functions\n\nBoth functions are in `packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport function getCloseCallRoundPda(roundId: Uint8Array): [PublicKey, number]\n// Seeds: [Buffer.from(\"cc_round\"), Buffer.from(roundId)]\n\nexport function getCloseCallConfigPda(): [PublicKey, number]\n// Seeds: [Buffer.from(\"closecall_config\")]\n```\n\n### Key Type Definitions\n\nFrom the IDL, the round account structure includes:\n\n- **BetEntry**: `{ player: pubkey, amount_lamports: u64 }`\n- **Outcome**: enum with variants `Pending | Green | Red | Refund`\n- **CloseCallPhase**: enum with variants `Open | Settled | Refunded`\n\nThe files are:\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.json`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/game-engine/src/closecall.ts`\n- `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/index.ts`"}],"totalDurationMs":10693,"totalTokens":42216,"totalToolUseCount":3,"usage":{"input_tokens":7,"cache_creation_input_tokens":16784,"cache_read_input_tokens":24732,"output_tokens":693,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":16784},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
