{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WW4EWX9A8Sn6WMA6YLDyWK","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile the comprehensive report:\n\n## Analysis Complete\n\nBased on my thorough review of the four requested files, here is the complete information:\n\n---\n\n### **1. CloseCallContext.tsx** (Full Content Provided Above)\n\n**Key Points:**\n- **Lines 29**: Imports `calculatePotentialPayout` from `../utils/payout-calculator`\n- **Lines 334, 354, 359**: Uses `calculatePotentialPayout()` in three places:\n  1. When building user history (line 334) - calculates payout for historical bets\n  2. When user already has a bet in current round (line 354) - shows their potential payout\n  3. When user is about to place a pending bet (line 359) - shows what they could win\n\n**placeBet Stub (Lines 376-405):**\n- Current implementation performs **local validation only**:\n  - Checks wallet connection (line 378)\n  - Validates bet side selection (lines 380-381)\n  - Validates bet amount against MIN/MAX (lines 383-388)\n  - Validates wallet balance (lines 390-392)\n- **TODO comment at line 397**: \"Build and send place_bet transaction via anchor-client (next iteration)\"\n- Currently does a dummy 500ms delay, then clears `pendingSide`\n- Sets `placingBet` loading state during the operation\n\n---\n\n### **2. mock-simulation.ts** (Full Content Provided Above)\n\n**Status**: **NOT IMPORTED ANYWHERE IN close-call**\n\n**What it contains:**\n- A complete mock game engine for Close Call (lines 1-441)\n- Manages round lifecycle: `open → settled/refunded`\n- Functions: `placeBet()`, subscription system, game init/stop, candle building\n- Uses `calculatePayouts()` and `determineOutcome()` from payout-calculator (line 18)\n- Emits events to boss-raid and player-profile event buses\n- Schedules 3-7 mock bets per round for testing\n\n**Key observation**: This file is self-contained and not referenced by CloseCallContext.tsx. The context fetches real data from backend API instead (`FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL`).\n\n---\n\n### **3. payout-calculator.ts** (Full Content Provided Above)\n\n**Status**: **ACTIVELY USED** - specifically `calculatePotentialPayout()`\n\n**Functions exported:**\n1. `determineOutcome(candle)` - Compares close vs open price → returns \"green\" | \"red\" | \"refund\"\n2. `calculatePayouts(pool, outcome)` - Returns all payouts and total fee for a resolved round\n3. `calculatePotentialPayout(betAmount, betSide, pool)` - **USED IN CONTEXT** - simulates bet payout before placement\n4. `calculateOddsMultiplier(side, pool)` - Calculates risk/reward ratio\n5. `calculatePoolDistribution(pool)` - Returns green/red percentages\n6. `formatAmount()` and `formatUsd()` - Display utilities\n\n**Payout Formula** (lines 4-8):\n```\ntotalPool = greenPool + redPool\nnetPool = totalPool × 0.97  (3% fee)\nplayerPayout = (playerBet / winningPool) × netPool\n```\n\n**Usage chain in CloseCallContext**:\n```\ncalculatePotentialPayout() is called with:\n  - betAmount: SOL amount\n  - betSide: \"green\" | \"red\"\n  - pool: PoolState (current round pools)\nReturns: potential SOL payout\n```\n\n---\n\n### **4. types.ts** (Full Content Provided Above)\n\n**Key type exports:**\n- `BetSide`: \"green\" | \"red\"\n- `RoundPhase`: \"open\" | \"settled\" | \"refunded\"\n- `CandleOutcome`: \"green\" | \"red\" | \"refund\"\n- `PlayerBet`: { address, side, amount, timestamp }\n- `PoolState`: { greenPool, redPool, totalPool, greenBets[], redBets[] }\n- `Round`: Complete round state with pool, phase, outcome, pricing\n- `CloseCallContextValue`: All context exports (state + actions)\n\n**Constants**:\n- `MIN_BET_AMOUNT = 0.001` SOL\n- `MAX_BET_AMOUNT = 100` SOL\n- `PLATFORM_FEE = 0.03` (3%)\n- `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 30000` (30 seconds)\n- `CANDLE_DURATION_MS = 60000` (60 seconds)\n\n---\n\n### **Summary: What Needs to Change for placeBet Implementation**\n\n| Component | Current State | What Needs to Change |\n|-----------|---------------|---------------------|\n| **CloseCallContext.placeBet** | Validation only + dummy delay | Replace dummy delay with anchor-client tx builder & submission |\n| **payout-calculator.ts** | Ready to use | No changes needed - already correct |\n| **mock-simulation.ts** | Unused in Context | Can stay as-is or be removed later (not blocking) |\n| **types.ts** | Complete type defs | No changes needed |\n\n**Key dependency for placeBet implementation**: The function will need to import and use the anchor-client (from `@rng-utopia/anchor-client`) to build and submit a CloseCall `place_bet` instruction with the address, round ID, side, and amount."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a7d782b13ace169d6 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 52938\ntool_uses: 17\nduration_ms: 39283</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"69ec7f4b-ea2c-48d6-9a60-da2ab1703b1a","uuid":"495a7440-b79e-42e3-ba4a-b9abe6dfca49","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these files completely:\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/context/CloseCallContext.tsx`\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/mock-simulation.ts`\n3. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/payout-calculator.ts`\n4. `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts`\n\nI need the full content of CloseCallContext.tsx to understand the current placeBet stub and what needs to change. Also need to see if mock-simulation.ts and payout-calculator.ts are still imported anywhere.\n\nThoroughness: very thorough.","agentId":"a7d782b13ace169d6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile the comprehensive report:\n\n## Analysis Complete\n\nBased on my thorough review of the four requested files, here is the complete information:\n\n---\n\n### **1. CloseCallContext.tsx** (Full Content Pr